review_title: Size up for looser, more relaxed fit
reviews:
I ordered a medium after reading other reviews about the sizing, and I’m glad I did! I normally wear a small and The medium i ordered is roomy and fits similarly to the picture.

The fabric is a soft and warm fleecy material, but definitely not high quality - which I wasn’t expecting for the price. A bit of a chemical scent upon opening the package, but it disappeared pretty quickly and was gone after a wash.

The stitching is pretty good, but there are definitely a few longer loose threads that hadn’t been snipped off.

4 stars because I ordered the sweater in grey, which in the image appears to be a lovely cool, pale grey - but in reality is a murky light green/grey - almost like when some cheap dyes fade in the sunlight.

I’ll still wear it, and overall I’m very happy with the purchase.
Item arrived exactly when they said it would - no hassle. Would purchase again.
